      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Gamedec",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " has a lot to overlook before one can enjoy it. It has a heavy cyberpunk aesthetic and a lot of varying environments, but all of that is overshadowed by the silliness of its concept. It reads to me like your character is such a hardcore alpha gamer that you can solve people’s problems by gaming. A complete and total removal of the word “game” from the script would do wonders for improving its image. The game already comes complete with a solution to that, focusing on calling it virtual reality. They even already have a word for it, virtualium. Unfortunately, ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Gamedec",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " has doubled down so hard on this concept that they named their game “",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Gamedec.”",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Its",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " story is its bread and butter by design, so it is unfortunate that it decided to sink itself with this choice.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
